Summary 11 of the book of Christian Theology

There are many theories of creation, such as creation based on materials, and creation from nothing.

The theory of creation based on existing materials means the creator is like a builder who brings order into the world. This theory was accepted by most gnostic, and some early theologians followed this theory. According to this theory, the evil and flaws of this world are not the fault of god but the fault of those materials.

The theory of creation from nothing believes God created all things from nothing, and thus, those creatures were originally good. In this theory, God created anything he wants to show his excellent capability. This theory was supported by Augustine of Hippo.

The theory of creation has some important meanings. Creation first means God is different from the creature, the creature is not holy. Creation second means God has the authority over the whole world, thus the human in His image bears the duty to take care of all creatures.

Creation third means the creature is good at first, because God saw the creature was good. However, this does not mean the creature is still perfect at now, because of the sin of Adam, the ground was cursed. Creation fourth means humanity was created in His own image.  

There are some models to explain God the Creator. The first model is emanation, an example is the sun which gives light. God is the source, the whole world was created by the flowing of His energy. Like the light of sun reflects the essence of the sun, the order of creation reflects the essence of God the Creator.

However, there are some flaws in the model of emanation. First is the unconsciousness of emanation, but God is not an unconscious existence. Second is the impersonality of this model, the personality of God cannot be conveyed through this model.

The second model is construction. There are many biblical verses that describe God as an excellent builder. However, according to this model, it seems God created this world based on existing materials, this conflicts with the theory of creation from nothing.

Another model is artistic presentation, for the creature was described as "God's work" by many christian thinkers. A good example is novel writing, for in this process, the writer created from nothing, and expressed his thoughts through his work.

Nowadays, because of the destruction of the ecosystem, many people accuse Christianity, because in the theory of creation, humanity has the superior authority over this world, thus encouraging the action of the exploitation of the world. However, according to the research of Genesis, humanity is not master of the world, but a steward of the world as the fellow worker of God.

There are 4 fundamental principles of the ecosystem in the book of Genesis: 1.God protects humans, thus humans shall protect his creature. 2.There shall be a sabbath for all creatures. 3.The capability of reproduction shall not be destroyed. 4.There is a boundary for humanity in the created world, in space and time.

One thing we cannot deny is that there is evil and suffering in this world. As we know, God is good, and he did not permit suffering or sins, but there is suffering and evil in this world, thus, does God not exist? Does God exist but not good?

Theodicy is such a theory to vindicate the goodness of God when evil exists in the world. According to Irenaeus of Lyons, humanity was not actually perfect, but with such potentiality to be perfect, thus, it's necessary to experience the good and the evil. In his words, the world is a valley to train spirit.

The special theory of Augustine of Hippo affected traditional theology a lot. Augustine was captured by Manicheism, in which materials were thought as evil, even the body of humanity. But Augustine denied this thought, he believes the creature of God is good originally. But, Where does evil come from?

The answer of Augustine is that evil comes from the misusing of the free will of humanity, because humans chose evil, thus the world was polluted by evil. However, where does the option of evil come from? Augustine put this responsibility to Satan, but cannot give a deeper answer about why God allowed Satan to become evil.

To solve such an unsolvable problem, Karl Barth proposed a whole new thought, to rethink all issues. Barth rejected the intuitive idea of "almighty", but supported the idea of the victory of the grace of God in the war with suffering and evil.

Alvin Plantinga gave another idea. In his words, free will is important, but without the option of evil, there is no free will. Thus, although God created the world as good as He can, God still gave the free will toward humans. Evil occurs here, humans selected evil, did evil in this world. In his word, the almighty of God is not the ability to do everything, but work in His self-limitation.

In recent years, the problem of suffering still remains as an important subject, here are some ideas in liberation theology, process theology, and the Old Testament.

In liberation theology, the suffering of poor people is not a passive event, but the struggle of God with suffering. In process theology, suffering and evil are from the self-limitation of God, because God uses only the ability of persuasion, to protect the free-will of humans.

In the Old testament, there are many verses expressing the resistance of suffering and evil. This resistance is the faith and belief towards God, which are precious in the eyes of God.

Theodicy tries to vindicate  the goodness of God in the evil world. But still, no one can give an answer to persuade everyone. In my opinion, God is good, this is not a vindication, but the essence of God. God is good, anything He has done is good, even evil in our eyes. God is good, such as "HE IS HE IS", this is essence, nothing behind this.














相对论并不禁止超光速的存在，而只是禁止「超越」光速。前者指的是速度大于光速的状态，后者指的是从亚光速加速至超光速的过程。
即所谓：亚光速的永远亚光速，超光速的永远超光速。

真实的普通物质都是亚光速的，所以通常才说光速是自然界速度的上限。
如果将快子一类物质也包括进来的话，则更普适的说法是：「光速」是一种速度的「屏障」或者「壁垒」，即
普通物质：质量为实数（质量平方为正数），速度比光速低，且永远不可向上超光速；
快子类物质：质量为虚数（质量平方为负数），速度比光速快，且永远不可向下亚光速。


虚数？唉呀，虚？嗯。。。唉。。。


最后需要指出，快子只是理论上的假想物质，至今没有任何实验证据。


质量为虚数是什么意思啊。吐槽一下虚数本来是解方程的工具，没想到后来竟被赋予了这么多实际意义。
